NAME
    App::GetoptLongUtils - Collection of CLI utilities related to
    Getopt::Long

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.006 of App::GetoptLongUtils (from Perl
    distribution App-GetoptLongUtils), released on 2017-08-10.

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution provides the following command-line utilities related
    to Getopt::Long:

    *   detect-getopt-long-script

    *   dump-getopt-long-evenless-script

    *   dump-getopt-long-script

    *   gen-getopt-long-spec-from-getopt-std-spec

    *   parse-getopt-long-spec

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-GetoptLongUtils>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-GetoptLongUtils>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-GetoptLongUtils>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

